programme.title: Tu Hai Mera Sunday ()
programme.desc: When local politician bans to play any kind of sport on the beach, 5 friends set out to find another place to play in the noisy, crowded Mumbai. It stars Barun Sobti & Shahana Goswami..(n)

programme.title: Raid
programme.desc: Period crime thriller revolves around a fearless income tax officer, who carries out a raid at the mansion of the powerful man in Lucknow. It stars Ajay Devgn and Ileana D'Cruz.(n)

programme.title: Mughal-E-Azam
programme.desc: The son and heir of the 16th-century emperor Akbar falls in love with a commoner. However, his father disapproves of his affection for a woman from such a lowly background and forbids him to marry her. Defying his father wishes causes the conflict between father and son to spiral into all-out war, and threatens to bring the empire to ruin. Indian historical epic, starring Dilip Kumar, Madhubala and Prithviraj Kapoor.(n)

programme.title: Luka Chuppi ()
programme.desc: It tells the story of a television reporter in Mathura who falls in love with a headstrong woman..(n)

programme.title: Hero
programme.desc: Sooraj, the son of gangster Suryakant Pasha, kidnaps Radha, the daughter of the chief of police. They fall in love after spending some time together but the police and Pasha's men keep chasing them.(n)

programme.title: Taarzan The Wonder Car
programme.desc: A car designer is murdered by a conspiracy of businessmen who stole his ideas. Years later, his son, now a college student, builds a futuristic car in honour of his dad. The vehicle becomes possessed by the spirit of his father, and goes on a rampage of revenge, leaving it's hapless owner to take the blame for a string of murders. Musical thriller, starring Vatsal Seth and Ayesha Takia.(n)

programme.title: Helicopter Eela ()

programme.title: Neerja
programme.desc: During a stopover at Karachi airport in Pakistan, Pan Am Flight 73 is stormed by four Palestinian terrorists belonging to the Abu Nidal Organisation. Flight attendant Neerja Bhanot immediately informs the flight crew, giving just enough warning for them to flee the plane, and she then puts her own life at risk in order to save the 359 passengers and fellow cabin crew. Fact-based thriller, starring Sonam Kapoor. In Hindi and English.(n)

programme.title: Ajnabee

After a party, Raj spends the night at his new friends' house, only to wake up the next morning with Sonia's dead body in his bed. When no one, not even his wife, believes he is innocent, he goes on the run to find the real killer. Thriller, starring Bobby Deol and Akshay Kumar.(n)
